    <lb n="1"/>Σαραπίωνι τῶν διαδόχων καὶ 

    <lb n="2"/>ὑποδιοικητῆι παρὰ Πτολεμαί-

    <lb n="3"/>ου Μακεδώνος τοῦ ὄντος ἐν κατοχῇ 

    <lb n="4"/>καὶ τῶν διδυμῶν. ἀποδεδομέ-

    <lb n="5"/>νης τῶι βασιλεῖ ἐντεύξεως 

    <lb n="6"/>ὑπὸ τῶν διδυμῶν <choice><corr>περ<supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">ὶ</supplied></corr><sic>περ</sic></choice> τῶν 

    <lb n="7"/>καθηκόντων αὐταῖς, ἧς κεχρημα-

    <lb n="8"/>τισμένης ἐπὶ σέ, σοῦ δὲ προσδε-

    <lb n="9"/>ηθέντος τῆς <choice><corr>παρὰ</corr><sic><add place="supralinear">υ</add>παρα</sic></choice> Δωρίων<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ος</supplied> 

    <lb n="10"/>τοῦ ἀντιγραφέως πρὸς ταῦ<add place="supralinear">τ</add>α 

    <lb n="11"/><choice><corr>ἀναφορᾶς</corr><sic>αναφοραν</sic></choice>, <choice><corr>ἧς</corr><sic><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/><add place="supralinear"><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/></add>ης</sic></choice> <add place="supralinear">ὑ</add>πὸ τοῦ ἀδελφοῦ 

    <lb n="12"/>μου ἀποδεδομένης σοι τῆι <num value="1">α</num> 

    <lb n="13"/>τοῦ Φαῶφι, καὶ συνηκολουθη-

    <lb n="14"/><choice><corr>κότος</corr><sic>συνηκολουθηκοτοι</sic></choice> σοι εἰς Πτολεμαίδα 

    <lb n="15"/>τοῦ Ἀρσινοίτου, συνέταξας· 

    <lb n="16"/>ὡς ἂν εἰς Μέμφιν. τῶν δὲ 

    <lb n="17"/>μεγίστων θεῶν καθ᾽ ἣν ἔ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">χ</supplied>εις 

    <lb n="18"/>εἰς αὐτοὺ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ς ἐ</supplied>κ προγονικῆς α<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ἱ</supplied>-

    <lb n="19"/>ρέσε<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ως</supplied> εὐσέβειαν 

    <lb n="20"/>ἀγειο<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">χ</supplied>ό<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">τ</supplied>ων <supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">σε</supplied> ἐπὶ τοὺς τόπους 

    <lb n="21"/>ἀξιῶ σε <choice><corr>ἐὰ<supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">ν φαίνηται</supplied></corr><sic>εα</sic></choice> ἀναλαβόντα 

    <lb n="22"/>τὸν παρὰ Δωρίωνος χρημα-

    <lb n="23"/>τισμὸν ἐπιτελέσαι 

    <lb n="24"/>ἀκολούθως. εὐτύχει. 

    <lb n="25"/><del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">μεν</del> 

    <lb n="26"/>Μεννίδει. ἐπισκεψάμενον 

    <lb n="27"/>ὅσα καθήκει ἀποδοῦναι. 

    <lb n="28"/><expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="20">κ</num> Ἁθὺρ <num value="2">β</num>. τοῖς <choice><corr>γραμματεῦσι</corr><sic>γραματευσι</sic></choice>. 

    <lb n="29"/><choice><corr>ἐπισκεψαμένους</corr><sic><subst><add place="inline">εψισκεψαμενους</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">εψισκεψαμενον</del></subst></sic></choice> ἀνενεγ-

    <lb n="30"/>κεῖν. 

    <lb n="31"/><expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="20">κ</num> <choice><corr>Ἁθὺρ</corr><sic>αθρυ</sic></choice> <num value="3">γ</num>. </ab></div><div n="meta.3413" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.3413" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" notAfter="-0162-12-03">vor 3. Dez. 162 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.3413" type="commentary" subtype="mentionedDates" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head><p>Z. 12-13: <date type="mentioned" value="-0162-11-02">2. Nov. 162 v.Chr.</date></p><p>Z. 28: <date type="mentioned" value="-0162-12-03">3. Dez. 162 v.Chr.</date></p><p>Z. 31: <date type="mentioned" value="-0162-12-04">4. Dez. 162 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.3413" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">UPZ</title><biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">22</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">3413</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0245</series>; <biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">22</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0245;1;22" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.3413" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><bibl type="illustration" default="NO">P.Lond. I, Facsimile 2</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.3413" type="bibliography" subtype="otherPublications" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Andere Publikation</head><bibl type="publication" subtype="other" default="NO">P.Lond. I 20 (S. 8)</bibl></div><div n="meta.3413